Confirmation / your mud-name(s)
-------------------------------

When we receive your money, we will confirm it via mud-mail. It is therefore
necessary that you write your mud-name on a piece of paper with the money. If
you want to receive a written receipt, print the mud-mail. And we also need
your mud-name so we can confirm the receipt and include your mud-name in the
list of contributors.
